A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a massive neon-lit warehouse filled with towering stacks of glowing shipping containers in electric blues and magentas, with a sleek autonomous robot methodically removing and dissolving older containers from the bottom shelves, leaving organized gaps behind. Holographic inventory numbers float above each container stack. Steam rises from vents in the industrial floor, and exposed pipes run along the ceiling. The scene conveys digital storage management through physical metaphor—the careful balance of accumulation and cleanup in a futuristic, atmospheric setting with dramatic rim lighting and deep shadows.
